dc_title_s: La principauté d'Orange et comitat de Venaissin.; La principavté d'Orange et comitat de Venaissin
dc_description_s: Relief shown pictorially. North oriented to bottom of map. Includes dedication to Prince Frederic Henry by Jodocus and Henricus Hondius. This state was published in atlases by Jan Jansson in 1630 and 1631-33. From the Jansson Appendix Atlas 1636-1680, title created to represent a unique collection within the Clark Library, University of Michigan. 1 map; 38 x 50 cm. This map is in the public domain. Please attribute access and use of this digitized map to the Stephen S. Clark Library, University of Michigan Library.
